buddies.name: Lenna
buddies.description: Wields rods and staves. Can use rare white magic abilities, buffing her Mind to cast potent healing magic, and supporting the party by managing their buffs and debuffs.

buddies.name: Elarra
buddies.description: Proficient with a variety of weapons, with a focus on rods and staves. Can use rare white magic abilities, buffing her Mind to cast potent healing magic, and supporting the party by managing their buffs and debuffs.

buddies.name: Faris
buddies.description: Proficient with a variety of weapons and armor, with a focus on spears and bows. Can use rare thief abilities, "stealing" stats from her enemies to buff her own.

buddies.name: Yehosua
buddies.description: Uses a variety of equipment and abilities, and has well-rounded stats. Suitable for multiple roles in battle.

buddies.name: Bartz
buddies.description: Proficient with a variety of weapons and armor, with a focus on daggers and heavy armor. Can use rare spellblade abilities, buffing his Attack to deal powerful physical elemental attacks.
